# Growvisi product rules

**Product:** WhatsApp-first revenue layer for Indian SMBs (1–20 people). Not a generic CRM.

## Non-negotiables

1. **Human replies from Growvisi Inbox** (or WhatsApp directly). Optional **Meta Business Agent** for first-line FAQ. Growvisi AI **classifies, tracks, assigns, alerts**, and may **auto-send guarded replies** when confident and grounded (`auto_guarded` mode on Growth+). It never auto-replies on sensitive topics, low confidence, or outside policy rails — those become drafts or human handoff.
2. **India-first:** INR pricing, Razorpay billing. No Stripe/USD in product UI.
3. **Enforce limits server-side** (`EntitlementsService`, `PLAN_LIMITS`). UI mirrors API; never UI-only gates.
4. **Honest automations:** no fake toggles for Meta-owned behavior (welcome = info card only).
5. **Onboarding is soft:** users can skip WhatsApp setup; `/dashboard/pricing` and settings always reachable.

## Out of scope for v1

Email CRM, SSO, in-app notification center, multi-channel inbox, Growvisi as chatbot.

## Terminology

Use `brand-copy.ts`: Conversations, Pipeline, Intelligence, Automations. Say ₹/mo and 14-day trial.

## Before adding features

Read `docs/GROWVISI-PRD.md`. Tie work to pipeline/revenue outcome. Prefer API + thin UI over large new modules.

